cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.NE 

The paper presents a scalable approach for semi-supervised learning on graph-structured data using convolutional neural networks. This work is related to machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), computer vision (cs.CV), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
